OL,7,FHarrowing stories from patients and
OL,8,FNHS workers who experienced the Covid-
OL,9,F19 pandemic have been published by the
OL,10,Finquiry examining its impact.
OL,12,FOver 32,000 people have contributed to
OL,13,Fthe Every Story Matters record,
OL,14,Fdesigned to assist UK Covid-19 Inquiry
OL,15,Fchairwoman Baroness Heather Hallett in
OL,16,Freaching conclusions and making
OL,17,Frecommendations on how to handle
OL,18,Ffuture pandemics.
