OL,7,FIt covers how patients found
OL,8,Fhealthcare access difficult, how
OL,9,Ffamilies faced significant challenges
OL,10,Fin supporting their loved ones at the
OL,11,Fend of life, and how health workers
OL,12,Ffelt planning for the pandemic was
OL,13,Fpoor and the speed of the response too
OL,14,Fslow.
OL,16,FThe document also includes detail from
OL,17,F604 in-depth interviews carried out
OL,18,Fwith those who were involved with
OL,19,Fhealthcare.
