OL,7,F"If you don't have that confidence,
OL,8,Fthat certainty and it's all a bit new
OL,9,Fto you and you're surrounded by chaos
OL,10,Fand suffering and death then I think
OL,11,Fit's much more stressful."
OL,13,FEnd-of-life care also frequently
OL,14,Finvolved hospital staff being with
OL,15,Fdying patients when their loved ones
OL,16,Fcould not.
OL,18,F"Nobody wants anybody to die on their
OL,19,Fown, and as nurses you try really hard
OL,20,Fto make sure that that doesn't
OL,21,Fhappen," one hospital nurse said.
