OL,7,F"If family members can't be there,
OL,8,Fyou're there. You just are. You just
OL,9,Fdo it."
OL,11,FThe document also showed how some
OL,12,Fmedics believed the Nightingale
OL,13,Fhospitals set up to treat patients was
OL,14,Fa misuse of resources.
OL,16,FOne said: "We set up huge Nightingale
OL,17,Fhospitals with ICU (intensive care)
OL,18,Fcapabilities which were under-used,
OL,19,Flikely due to lack of highly trained
OL,20,Fstaff or ICU need.
