OL,8,Fmeant these being used for less
OL,9,Fintensive care such as care of the
OL,10,Felderly, rehab beds or Covid+
OL,11,Fintermediate care beds, freeing up
OL,12,Fhospital beds for patients that needed
OL,13,Fthem."
